flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Production start and completion events, incoming material receipt notifications.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Collect production stage data]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Cortex Monitoring - Analyze production data for quality issues]
  N2 --> N3{PB: CWB Lifecycle - Decide on quality gate inspections and rework management}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4[PB: Remote Functions - Execute quality checks and rework actions]
  N4 --> N5[PB: UI Screens - Review quality control plans and adherence]
  N5 --> N6[PB: Notification - Notify stakeholders of quality issues and actions]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced waste, minimized rework delays, improved first-pass yields, and enhanced overall production quality.]
  N3 -->|High defect rate detected| B1[Increase inspection frequency]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Improved defect detection]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Low defect rate detected| B2[Decrease inspection frequency]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Optimized inspection costs]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Critical non-conformance identified| B3[Initiate root cause analysis]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Corrective actions implemented]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]